local skynet = require "skynet_plus"
local base = require "base"

require"printfunc"

require "normal_enum"

local monitor_lib = require "monitor_lib"

local urllib = require "http.url"

local CMD=base.CMD
local DATA=base.DATA
local PUBLIC=base.PUBLIC


function PUBLIC.decode_func(c)
	return string.char(tonumber(c, 16))
end

function PUBLIC.url_decode(str)
	if type(str) ~= "string" then
		return ""
	end
	local str = str:gsub('+', ' ')
	return str:gsub("%%(..)", PUBLIC.decode_func)
end

function CMD.shoping_gold_pay(_data)
	local ok, arg = xpcall(function ()
		return cjson.decode(_data)
	end,
	function (error)
		print(error)
	end)

	if not ok then
		return nil,1001
	end	
	
	local shoping_desc = PUBLIC.url_decode(arg.shoping_desc)
	--urllib.parse_query(arg.shoping_desc)
	DATA.shoping_desc_debug = DATA.shoping_desc_debug or {}
	table.insert(DATA.shoping_desc_debug,shoping_desc)
	
	return CMD.user_shoping_gold_pay(
		arg.user_id,
		arg.amount,
		arg.order_id,
		shoping_desc,
		arg.goods_id,
		arg.authflags)
end


return function()

	return basefunc.tostring(DATA.shoping_desc_debug)

end

-- 清除 上一期数据（新一期开始）。 注意：此前要做好手工备份
-- 参数 _os ： ios 或 android
function CMD.reset_cpl_game_info(_os)

	if _os ~= "ios" and _os ~= "android" then
		return "param error!"
	end

	-- 确定 ios 用户（其他的就是 安卓用户）
	local _sql = PUBLIC.format_sql([[select id from player_register where market_channel = 
			%s and (register_os like '%%iPhone%%' or register_os like '%%iOS%%')]],DATA.market_channel)	

	local ret = PUBLIC.db_query(_sql )
	local ios_users = {}
	for _,v in ipairs(ret) do
		ios_users[v.id] = true
	end

	local _reset_data =
	{
		ddz_round_count=0,
		payment=0,
		win_jingbi=0,
		old_player=1,
	}

	local _count = 0
	local _count_total = 0
	for _id,_ in pairs(LL.player_data) do
		if ("ios" == _os and ios_users[_id]) or ("ios" ~= _os and not ios_users[_id]) then
			PUBLIC.update_cpl_data(_id,_reset_data)
			_count = _count + 1
		end

		_count_total = _count_total + 1
	end

	return {true,os=_os,count_total=_count_total,deal_count=_count}
end

return function()
	return "ok"
end
